Various demos and tools for EAD validation and processing:

ead-schematron: Schematron schemata to demonstrate rules checking of EAD instances

* ead_rules-iso.sch: ISO Schematron schema to demonstrate rules checking of EAD instances 

* ead_rules.sch: Schematron 1.5 schema to demonstrate rules checking of EAD instances

ead-tidy: XSLT 2.0 Stylesheet to perform various "tidying" procedures on EAD instances 

extend-with-nvdl: demonstration of use of NVDL to extend EAD by allowing elements from external namespaces

strip-ns: XSLT 2.0 stylesheet for converting EAD 2002 RNG-valid or XSD-valid instance to HTML using the eadcbs8.xsl stylesheet (though any EAD(DTD) to XML stylesheet could be used)